data.description: Indulge in the ultimate living experience with this exceptional tri-level home. Revel in the spaciousness of 3 well-appointed bedrooms and 2 full baths, providing comfort and privacy for the entire family. The heart of the home is the expansive family room, a perfect hub for relaxation and socializing.The eat-in kitchen is a culinary haven, seamlessly opening into the living room area, creating a dynamic space for entertaining and family gatherings. Imagine the joy of preparing meals while staying connected with loved ones. The convenience continues with a dedicated laundry room, ensuring efficiency in your daily routine. The double lot offers a vast outdoor space for various activities. This residence is not just a home; it's a haven of comfort and style. Embrace the lifestyle you've always desired - schedule a viewing today!"
